inscription:
Inscriptions, Title, Date, Mark

Red chalk, along border of medallion: [DUM PELAGO DESAEVIT HIEMS / MARINE / 1744];

UL corner of old blue mount, in pen and brown ink: [remis le dessein a M. / Marteau le 26 9bre [Septembre] / 1743];

Verso, on white paper, in pen and brown ink; [15]
